4Geeks Academy offers a Cybersecurity Bootcamp designed for aspiring cybersecurity specialists with no prior knowledge. The program covers essential topics including Windows, Linux, network, and server administration. Students will learn cloud security, penetration testing, and threat intelligence analysis, while mastering risk management and compliance with standards like ISO 27001 and NIST. The bootcamp is 16 weeks long, featuring three live online classes per week with a maximum of 16 participants. No prior experience is needed, and classes are available in both English and Spanish. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate, recognized by various institutions. For more information, visit https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/cybersecurity. stop